::Ramulus::

Ramulus looks at SnowCat. "Nice to meet you," he says, "My name's Ramulus."

He looks her over. "You can get some food at the Ark, if its still intact. If 
not, I can take you to base."

He was still keeping track of the other bot in the bushes, ready to react if 
neccessary.
